                <note rend="inline" type="source">871.6363/176: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Rumania</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Jay</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bucharest</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-06-29T21:00:00+01:44">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 29, 1924—9 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received June 30—3:49 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>27. Parliament has just passed mining bill. The bill now remains to be signed by
                    the King. Will report fully by mail.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jay</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
